OL,3,GOPINIONCThe return of Loose Women sees
OL,4,Clunchtime news move back to 1.30pm
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe ITV Lunchtime News is on the move `
OL,7,Fagain.
OL,9,FIt returns to 1.30pm on 27th April with
OL,10,Fthe regional news following at 1.55pm.
OL,12,FNeedless to say, this is because Loose
OL,13,FWomen is back from its break in its
OL,14,Fnormal 12.30pm slot.
OL,16,FSo it seems the news will move whenever
OL,17,FLoose Women is off.
OL,19,FIt may make practical sense to do this
OL,20,Fbut moving the news in this way sends
OL,21,Fout the wrong signals about ITV's
OL,22,Fpriorities.
OL,23,EPub: 17-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,146,140,200,120,0,100
