OL,3,GOPINIONCThe return of Loose Women sees
OL,4,Clunchtime news move back to 1.30pm
OL,5,
OL,6,FOf course, those of us with long
OL,7,Fmemories remember when the BBC's
OL,8,Flunchtime news moved about.
OL,10,FUntil 1986 it preceded Pebble Mill at
OL,11,FOne from September until May ` latterly
OL,12,Fat 12.30pm ` and moved to a later slot
OL,13,Fin the summer months.
OL,15,F1pm became the standard summer time in
OL,16,F1982 and the regular time when a full
OL,17,Fdaytime schedule began in 1986.
OL,19,FBut at least there were practical
OL,20,Freasons for this.
OL,23,EPub: 17-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,146,140,200,120,0,100
