OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F145A1777206670
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe return of Loose Women sees
OL,4,Clunchtime news move back to 1.30pm
OL,5,
OL,6,FIpm was a better time in the summer. An
OL,7,Fearlier slot would have meant the
OL,8,Fprogramme moving regularly for sport.
OL,10,FPebble Mill at One was
OL,11,Fwell-established, and very popular with
OL,12,Fthose at home during the day, by the
OL,13,Ftime the BBC started to take lunchtime
OL,14,Fnews provision seriously.
OL,16,FBut back to the present on ITV.
OL,18,FWill the Lunchtime News be back at
OL,19,F12.30pm when Loose Women takes its next
OL,20,Fbreak?
OL,23,EPub: 17-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
